strings: <voice_0x01000EBE><se_def>The prince Carlos: This old smelly car is too small for me!
<voice_0x01000EBF><se_def>The prince Carlos: When you take out the garbage, your feet get tired.
<voice_0x01000EC0><se_def>The prince Carlos: There are good and bad! What two people will go on a trip together?
<voice_0x01000EC1><se_low>January: This is my Grandpa! When I said yes, I cut my hair! - I'm the king, fool!
<voice_0x01000EC2><se_low>King of tricks: I got a little closer
<voice_0x01000EC3><se_low>King of tricks: evidence! You can't even tell that she's turned into a mare!
<voice_0x01000EC4><se_low>King of tricks: For now, it's best to keep the truth a secret. Make sure everybody knows how to hide it.
<voice_0x01000EC5><se_low>King of tricks: Fairies! what will happen to us
<voice_0x01000EC6><se_def>The prince Carlos: The bastard's name is "Carlo"! Dongfang finally took the royal family to the hunting grounds. this is the start
<voice_0x01000EC7><se_def>The prince Carlos: Some exercise! And before I forget it, <hero>...
<voice_0x01000EC8><se_def>The prince Carlos: The bottle contains a powder that masks the bad human odour. Must be sprayed before going to the fishmonger.
<voice_0x01000EC9><se_def>The prince Carlos: Lizards are very sensitive to smell. If they discover what we are hiding, they will run away.
<voice_0x01000ECA><se_def>The prince Carlos: So, to fight against a lizard, you need to smell its smell.
<voice_0x01000ECB><se_def>The prince Carlos: I have to do it myself, I'll stay in the car until I get there.
<voice_0x01000ECC><se_def>The prince Carlos: You have arrived and you have to leave. Keep going!
